  "title": "AN ACT TO AMEND TITLES 6 AND 21 OF THE DELAWARE CODE RELATING TO RENTAL CARS AND PEER- TO-PEER CAR SHARING LOSS OF USE.",
  "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}",
